summary: This file, CortexAlgorithmsUtil.h, is a part of the SMG_NothingIsAll codebase and contains methods for performing various algorithms using the Cortex framework. The class CortexAlgorithmsUtil inherits from NSObject in Foundation and provides a method maxOfLoopValue:ds: which takes two strings as arguments and returns a double value.
